        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-31" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#601414);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);movable=1;resizable=1;rotatable=1;deletable=1;editable=1;locked=0;connectable=1;strokeWidth=3;align=center;fontColor=default;fontSize=30;" value="Critérios de Aceitação" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="290" width="280" x="210" y="390" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-32" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;blockquote style=&quot;margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,6,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,6,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,6,1,0&quot;&gt;Média&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="1260" x="491" y="-180" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-33" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,7,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;1. O treinador tem de estar autenticado e associado à equipa para a qual pretende partilhar o material.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,7,1,2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;2. O módulo de armazenamento de ficheiros do servidor (ou integração na &lt;i data-path-to-node=&quot;1,7,1,2&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;72&quot;&gt;cloud&lt;/i&gt;) tem de estar configurado&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;e com espaço disponível.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="240" width="1260" x="491" y="-120" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-34" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;br&gt;&lt;span data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;1. O plano de treino ou o ficheiro multimédia é armazenado de forma segura e associado logicamente à&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;equipa (ou a uma sessão de treino específica).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,1,2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;2. Os atletas da equipa passam a ter acesso imediato (em modo de leitura/visualização) aos materiais&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;partilhados no seu portal.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,8,1,4&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;3. É gerada uma notificação (opcional) para os atletas informando da disponibilização de novo material&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;tático.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="270" width="1260" x="490" y="120" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ZR-NAflUI1GGsINpZlQH-35" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=light-dark(#A20025,#FFFFFF);strokeColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);strokeWidth=3;fontColor=light-dark(#000000,#000000);align=left;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=25;" value="&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,9,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;1. O módulo de upload de ficheiros deve aceitar formatos comuns de vídeo (ex: MP4) e documentos (ex:&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;PDF, imagens), impondo um limite máximo de tamanho por ficheiro.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,9,1,2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;2. O treinador deve ter a capacidade de associar um plano de treino diretamente a uma sessão já&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;agendada no calendário.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,9,1,4&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;3. O sistema tem de garantir o isolamento da informação, impedindo categoricamente que atletas ou&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;treinadores de equipas adversárias (ou de outros escalões) acedam à biblioteca tática dessa equipa.&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="290" width="1260" x="490" y="390" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
